es.Losing, winning.\n\n- Lailah Gifty Akita, Think Great: Be Great!\n|\nLove is a weapon of Light, and it has the power to eradicate all forms of darkness. That is the key. When we offer love even to our enemies, we destroy their darkness and hatred...\n\n- Yehuda\n|\nSometimes, we are simply trapped in the cage of our own emotions, unable to break those bars. It hurts!\n\n- Tarang Sinha, We Will Meet Again...\n|\nWithout being push to the wall, we will have remained in our comfortable zone. But this circumstance challenges us to find the courage to move on.\n\n- Lailah Gifty Akita, On Eagles Wings:Rise\n|\nNo matter what, if you have the strength of life, it is enough to be thankful.\n\n- Lailah\n|\nI am a dead man, that's all......My Brain doesn't workproperly.My Brain is diagonessed officially dead....\n\n- Deyth Banger, Notes Of A Dead Man Sequel\n|\nWhat are you doing?” I asked Loretta. “Stabbing a cushion,” she told me.\n\n- Joel N. Ross, The Lost Compass\n|\nI have to teach myself. I kind of wish I'd continued with my education, but that's something I can do in the future.\n\n- Billie\n|\nA girl in a bikini is like having a loaded gun on your coffee table- There's nothing wrong with them, but it's hard to stop thinking about.\n\n- Garrison\n|\nIt only takes a tenth grade course on evolution to know that the prostate g-spot’s existence alone is proof that ass play has been done for a very, very long time.\n\n- Maggie\n|\nAt first, I was lost in you, but now you're lost on me.\n\n- Ahmed\n|\nSomehow, we have gotten off track from the basics of health and spirituality, and we get in our own way.\n\n- Alice McCall, Wellness Wisdom - Inspired by One Woman's Journey with Breast Cancer\n|\nMiss Leefolt sigh, hang up the phone like she just don't know how her brain gone operate without Miss Hilly coming over to push the Think buttons.\n\n- Kathryn Stockett, The Help\n|\nWhenever we make the choice to bring fear into the light with truth-seeking questions, we shall fi